{
  "title": "Creamy Russian Dried Shrimp Bisque",
  "description": "A savory and comforting Russian dish made with dried shrimp, this bisque is a great hangover cure and is FODMAP friendly. It features a rich and creamy texture with a shattering flavor.",
  "cuisine": "Russian",
